            <title>[SPR-12603] Introduce declarative customization of ApplicationContext before refresh in the TestContext framework</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-12603</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be very nice for creating custom test annotations if we could get access to the &lt;tt&gt;GenericApplicationContext&lt;/tt&gt; before it&apos;s loaded.&lt;/p&gt;

